data.description: Can you say Home Galore! This amazing home has an abundance of space for the growing family! It sits on a quiet country road not far from Capac, Yale, Brockway and Emmett with plenty of wildlife to enjoy!  It features 4 spacious bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, a study/office, a huge bonus room that could be used as a 5th bedroom that has its own heat pump and A/C and a finished huge attic for all your storage. It has a spacious open floor plan with plenty of windows that bring in the sunlight and tall ceilings in some of the rooms. It also features a spacious finished walkout basement with a possible 6th bedroom and a family recreation or game room for the entire family get togethers.  It has a second floor laundry room and a spacious backyard for family cookouts and bonfires!  It also has a generator for electricity if the homeowner loses power. All appliances are included and the outdoor wood burning furnace. What are you wait for? Make that appointment, grab your keys and come out out today!    BTVAI
